snippet: Aaron Cook, ranked No. 1 in the world in his weight class, was left off the team in favor of Lutalo Muhammad, who is No. 59 in the same weight class.
abstract: British Olympic Assn is reviewing British Taekwondo's Olympic athlete selection process after Aaron Cook, ranked No. 1 in his weight class, is left off the 2012 team in favor of Lutalo Muhammad, who is ranked No. 59 in the same weight class.
lead_paragraph: Aaron Cook, ranked No. 1 in the world in his weight class, was left off the team in favor of Lutalo Muhammad, who is No. 59 in the same weight class.
